  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Story]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > \"Under the Streetlights of the Reiche\" is an omnibus-style adventure game. Experience the last day a man spends in this city. A good man who is well-liked by those around him loses his job and has to leave the town he has lived in for a long time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3607020/extras/0fdc26fd7a161d24f613d86201359d76.poster.avif?t=1769788026\" width=800 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3607020/extras/0fdc26fd7a161d24f613d86201359d76.webm?t=1769788026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3607020/extras/0fdc26fd7a161d24f613d86201359d76.mp4?t=1769788026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Overview]</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By clicking on objects on the screen, the story will progress with immersive images and sounds. Enjoy reading the characters' thoughts. Use the various hints within the game to guide you to the story's conclusion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3607020/extras/769b017a5431efc076a538ed37d73719.poster.avif?t=1769788026\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3607020/extras/769b017a5431efc076a538ed37d73719.webm?t=1769788026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3607020/extras/769b017a5431efc076a538ed37d73719.mp4?t=1769788026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > [Features] </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of movies and sounds will give you an immersive experience. Your choices will help you discover the hidden truth.</p>",
